<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.5.1">
<l>veruvātāḷ vāyveruvi vēṅkaṭamē vēṅkaṭamē yeṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>maruvāḷā leṉkuṭaṅkāl vāṇeṭuṅkaṇ tuyilmaṟantāḷ vaṇṭār koṇṭal</l>
<l>uruvāḷaṉ vāṉavarta muyirāḷa ṉolitirainīrp pauvaṅ koṇṭa</l>
<l>tiruvāḷa ṉeṉmakaḷaic ceytaṉaka ḷeṅṅaṉamnāṉ cintik kēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She who is [usually] fearless, her lips [now] trembling,</l>
<l rend="indent">in truth  calls, “Vēṅkaṭa, Vēṅkaṭa!”</l>
<l>She will not cuddle [on] my lap at all; she shun sleep</l>
<l rend="indent">[for her] long spear-like eyes.</l>
<l>He who is the color of full clouds and bees,</l>
<l rend="indent">he who rules of the lives of the celestials,</l>
<l>Tiru’s lord who resembles the sea waters with roaring waves,</l>
<l rend="indent">how do I [even] think of what [he] did  to my daughter?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
